Redis

In Memory data base
Faster since because its in-memory
it can be scaled.
provides high availablity


Redis Installation - Mac

1. Install home brew

/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)"

2. Update home Homebrew

brew update

3. Install Redis

brew install redis.

4. un-installation of redis.

brew uninstall redis.

5. starting redis server

brew services start redis.

6. stopping redis server

brew services stop redis.


Note :
To List All keys : keys *
To flush all values : flushAll


The History of the commands executed is present in directory : ~/rediscli_history

Any failure in redis happens via the .log file (the configuration is made in the redis.config)
